      "content": "### 1) ANALYZE the molecular structure\n**SMILES:** `CCSc1ccc2c(c1)N(CCCN1CCN(C)CC1)c1ccccc1S2 . O=C(O)C[C@@H](O)C(=O)O . O=C(O)C[C@@H](O)C(=O)O`",
