      "step_index": 7,
      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "The **salt form (malate)** will keep the amine protonated in formulation, but in vivo the equilibrium still supports a significant fraction of protonated species at physiological pH\u2014consistent with CYP2D6 binding.",
